sentences.sContent: She went solo backpacking for eight months in the Australian outback.
sentences.sCn: 她在澳大利亚内陆独自背包旅行了八个月。

sentences.sContent: Whoever they are, they will never know that they are a blood brother or sister to an Australian! ＃
sentences.sCn: 不管他们是谁，他们绝不会知道自己是一个澳大利亚人的血亲兄弟或姐妹。

phrases.pCn: n. 澳大利亚牧羊犬；澳洲牧羊犬

trans.tranCn: 澳大利亚的；澳大利亚人的
trans.tranOther: relating to Australia or its people
